title: 101 Offline Activities You Can Do With Your Child
description:
101 Offline Activities You Can Do With Your Child

Author(s): 	Steve Bennett, Ruth Bennett
Date: 	2012 	
Format: 	EPUB 
Language: 	English 	
ISBN10: 	0984228527

Here's a brief time out that EVERYONE in your family will enjoy: disconnect from the Net, put away your digital toys, and get ready for some good old-fashioned fun. Even 20 minutes a day can be rejuvenating for you and a great way to connect with your children. In "101 Offline Activities You Can Do With Your Child," you'll find activities that tap the most advanced microprocessor   the one behind the ears. Best of all, you can do most of the activities with little or no preparation!
